simmoa is an Erlang based MUD
=============================

License: 
-----------------------------
The code is released under the MIT license.


Installation:
-----------------------------
Still learning how to do packaging etc in Erlang, work in progress ;)


Running:
-----------------------------
if all the files are compiled, then type in the Erlang repl:
application:start(simmoa).


Use:
-----------------------------
Telnet to port 5555. 
Enter a player name when prompted. 
Then any further input is interpreted as game commands.


Feedback:
-----------------------------
is most welcome!
